    public class VKApiPhotoSize
extends VKApiModel
implements java.lang.Comparable<VKApiPhotoSize>, android.os.Parcelable, Identifiable
    Describes an photo info in special format. Some methods returns information about copies of the original image in different sizes, Represented as an array of sizes, containing a description of the objects of this class.
